Electrical problems in Srinagar homes should never be ignored. Flickering lights, tripping breakers, or warm switch plates can signal wiring issues that need a **qualified electrician**.

## When to call an electrician

- Frequent MCB or fuse trips
- Burning smell near switches or sockets
- Sparks when plugging in appliances
- New fan or light installation
- Inverter or backup power connections
- Full home wiring check before renovation

## Do not DIY these jobs

High-voltage wiring, panel work, and outdoor connections require proper tools and experience. Booking through Panun Kaergar connects you with **verified electricians** who serve your area in Srinagar.

